text:
Drake 'gets over Jennifer Lopez split and moves on with Winnie Harlow' The singer was spotted getting cosy with the model at a London nightclub Share Is Drake dating Winnie Harlow? Drake has been linked to model Winnie Harlow after they were spotted partying together at a London nightclub. 
The Hotline Bling singer was seen dancing intimately with the Canadian beauty, according to The Sun. 
The star, who has been in London for a string of gigs at the O2, was reportedly getting cosy with Winnie at Libertine nightclub where he was hosting a private party until 5am on Sunday. 
A fellow party-goer told the newspaper: "Jourdan Dunn and Adriana Lima were at the bash too but Drake only had eyes for Winnie. The pair were spotted chatting and dancing together. Read More Drake hosted a VIP party at a London club (Photo: Rex Features) Winnie was reportedly partying with Drake at a London club on Saturday night (Photo: Getty) 
"Winnie's night started at West End club Cirque Le Soir but she quickly left the club to meet up with Drake at Libertine, which is nearby. 
"They've always been friends, with Drake even rapping about Winnie on his track Know Yourself, but they looked particularly close on Saturday night." 
Drake has previously dated Jennifer Lopez . 
The unlikely pair shocked the showbiz world - and Drake's ex, Rihanna - when they revealed they were enjoying a romance late last year. They then confirmed their relationship earlier this month.
